body:
"Lots'a Gunz" is a datapack that introduces a variety of "gunz"(really cool guns), and a lot of new items, structures and mobs!

Version RE8 BETA 1.0.0 adds (long one, prepare yourselves):

# General

-Re-added half of the gunz and items;

-Added IDs to all the items in the datapack;

-All items from the datapack can keep their modifiers and work as normal;

-Added Auto-Reload option (by default, it reloads the datapacks every 10 minutes, but the player can choose 5, 10 or 30 minutes; it is used to refresh and remove useless data);

-Re-sorted the 'Get Items' structure chests;

-Reworked half of the function system for better optimization;

-Reworked some advancements;

-Improved friendly-fire and added death messages;

-Foxes weren't damaged by gunz;

-The Ender Dragon will be killed correctly by gunz now;

-Minecraft advancements that require killing a mob can now be completed if killed with gunz or grenadez from this datapack;

-Auto-Smelt Enchantment now works with all Raw Ores;

-The Gunz Trophy requires to get all gunz (if the player gets the enchanted or ELITE version of the original gun, it still counts as that gun);

-Changed the 'look' of the Gunz's Altar Books;

-The ELITE Difficulty now increases the health and attack damage of all hostile mobs in Minecraft and this datapack;

-Added <u>**NEW**</u> DMGNULLGUNZT;


### <u>**List of re-added stuff:**</u>

-Laser Gun and its enchant;

-Triple Shotgun and its enchant;

-Tikelatos Blowpipe;

-AFT-95 and its enchant;

-Bang Piztol and its enchant;

-Mini-gunzt and its skin;

-'Ash'thrower;

-Cannonball;

-Normal, Poisonous and Slowness Clayballs;

-Ancient Fire Turtle Shell;

-Small Bullet and Small Bullets;

-Bottle of Ash;

-Battery;

-Soul's Ash;

-Gunz Wrench;

-Tracker;

-Gunz Crate;

-All Books of Gunz's Altar (except Vol.II, Double Duplicator and 'Bouncy' enchant);

-Boots of Mobility;

-Night Glasses and its broken form;

-Auto-Smelting Enchant;

-Woodanlanchops Grenadez;

-Ancient Fire Turtle;

-Gunz Soldier's Soul;

-Acacia Bug;

-Lil' Muncher;

-Abandoned Chest;

-Sky Thing;

-Woodanlan;


# **Crafting**

-Now plays a sound when the player crafts or fuses items;

-Changed recipe for Gunz Wrench;

-The player can craft one piece of ammo (Cannonball, Clayballs, etc.) or a stack (64) of ammo by placing the maximum amount of materials needed for the stack;

-When the player repairs a gun, it will keep the stats and modifiers that it had instead of having half of ammo, total ammo, etc.;

-The player can now craft 2 Cannonballs instead of 1;

-Changed recipe for Triple Shotgun and Broken Triple Shotgun;

-Changed recipe for Broken 'Multiwave' Triple Shotgun;

-The player can now craft 4 Clayballs instead of 1;

-Changed recipe for Slowness Clayball;

-Added recipe for Weakness Clayball (the old recipe of Slowness Clayball);

-Added recipe for Wither Clayball (it is crafted with Poisonous Clayballs and Wither Roses);

-Added recipe for Cursed Clayball (it is crafted with Wither Clayballs and Echo Shards);

-Changed recipe for Bottle of Ash (15 max Bottles of Ash when the player crafts a stack);

-Changed recipe for Broken AFT-95;

-Changed recipe for Broken 'Guided' AFT-95;

-Changed recipe for Tracker;

-Crafted Auto-Smelt Pickaxes now keep its modifiers(Enchantments, Name, etc);

-Changed recipe for Broken Night Glasses;

-Changed recipe for Broken 'Ash'thrower;

-The player can now craft 2 Small Bullets instead of 1;

-Changed recipe for Small Bullet;

-Added recipe for Small Bullets (5 max Small Bullets when the player crafts a stack);


# **Fusing**

-Changed 'Gunz Updater' to NEW 'Gunz Fuser' (the player can fuse 2 items to create a better item);

-Added <u>**NEW**</u> Armored Elytra;


# **Items**

### Gunz Wrench:

-It has 88 durability and will now break when it reaches 0 durability (used to break randomly);

### Tracker:

-It detects Gunz Structures more smoothly now;

-The arrow spawns around the player;

-Now it pings the player a sound if it is closer to a Gunz Structure;

### Gunz Crate:

-Reworked the roll system;

-Changed rarities roll chance:

Nothing: 10%; <br>
Common: 30%; <br>
Rare: 27.5%; <br>
Epic: 20%; <br>
Legendary: 12.5%;

-Added pity system to the Gunz Crate(the player can see it on its Gunz Wrench; after 10 openings, the player will get a guaranteed Epic Gun; after 60 openings, the player wil get a guaranteed Legendary Gun);

-If both Epic and Legendary pities are next, the Legendary Pity has priority first, and next case Epic Pity has priority;

-Slightly increased the chances of finding a Gunz Crate in the Sky Thing (until The Light Force Executioner is added back);

### Boots of Mobility:

-Speed boost applies instantly now;

-Made them break now;

### Night Glasses:

-It now activates depending on the light level the player is on (between 0 and 4 light level);

-Temporarily added the Broken Night Glasses to the Woodanlan Chests;

### Small Bullet and Small Bullets:

-Changed the 'look' of the Small Bullets;

-Temporarily added Small Bullet and Small Bullets to the Woodanlan Chests;

### <u>NEW</u> Armored Elytras:

-The player can fuse Elytras with Diamond or Netherite Chestplates and will get the stats and enchants of the chestplate (so that the player can be fully armored while also flying);


# **Mobs**

-The player can spawn the mobs like vanilla mobs with spawn eggs ('Get Items' only, except for Lil' Muncher);

-Added particle effects to mobs and hit detection;

### Ancient Fire Turtle:

-Has 30 health now (both difficulties);

-Now spawns by eating Piglins instead of Zombified Piglins;

-It is now passive in ELITE DIFFICULTY;

-Always drops an Ancient Fire Turtle Shell in ELITE DIFFICULTY (and a small chance to drop the ELITE AFT Mini-gunzt);

### Gunz Soldier's Soul:

-It now moves slower towards the player to launch a surprise attack;

### Acacia Bug:

-Doesn't drop Stinky Dust until next update;

### Lil' Muncher:

-It is now craftable;

-When placed down, it will summon a player-made Lil' Muncher, which the player can defend itself against enemies;

-The player can also wear the Lil' Muncher on its head to protect itself from player-made Lil' Munchers and also detect them from a distance of 10 blocks (if the player stays on a redstone block while wearing it, it will take damage);

-It will suck the entities from a distance of 3 blocks, and they also get sparked if they are in a distance of 7 blocks (this is to tell the players if they are close to it);

-It can now also be killed if no block is underneath it (it will drop an iron ingot), but it will not be destroyed by arrows anymore (it will eat them);

-To place it down and do damage, the player has to spawn it on a Redstone Block;


# Structures

### Abandoned Chest:

-Now it has a 50% chance to spawn during morning in the Overworld underneath the player's feet, after the first day has passed in the player's world;

-Because of the change above => Removed the red outline of the chest;

### Gunz Altar:

-When the player enchants a gun, the gun keeps its stats and modifiers now (before it added max ammo);

-Its fires will only dissipate if the structure is destroyed;

### Gunz Ruin:

-Now naturally generates like vanilla structures;

-It generates in deserts, the same as Desert Pyramids;

### The Sky Thing:

-Now naturally generates like vanilla structures;

-It generates above oceans, a little bit rare to find it;

-Changed the structure;

-Changed the lock on the big chest;

-When the player unlocks the big chest, the bedrock will transform to dirt;

### The Woodanlan:

-Now naturally generates like vanilla structures;

-It generates the same as a Pillager Outpost, but more common;

-Added Mangrove and Cherry Wood to the collection (not used in the puzzle);

-Reworked the reward room;


# Gunz, Gunz Reworks and Grenadez Reworks

**bosses include the Elder Guardian, Ender Dragon, 'Endermosis'(not added yet), Warden and Wither;* <br><br>

-Gunz will play a sound when they are ready to fire;

### <u>**NEW**</u> DMGNULLGUNZT:

-When used on a non-player mob (except bosses), it will toggle their immunity to Gunz and Grenadez (but not 'vanilla' explosions from the gunz);

-When in hand, it shows all the immune mobs to Gunz and Grenadez in a range of 10 blocks radius;

-25 blocks range;

-Unlimited uses, ammo and no cooldown;

-It can be used only on Creative Mode;

-It is obtainable only from the 'Get Items' structure;

### Laser Gun:

-Changed the laser sound, so that it sounds different from the 'TNT' Laser Gun;

-Changed how it shoots: it shoots instantly now;

-25 blocks range;

-Deals 60 damage to all mobs;

-Changed ammo from 15 to 5;

### 'TNT' Laser Gun:

-Changed how it shoots: it shoots instantly now;

-25 blocks range;

-Deals 60 damage to all mobs;

-Changed ammo from 7 to 5;

### Triple Shotgun:

-Each Cannonball deals 6 damage to all mobs;

-13 blocks range;

-The player can add as many Cannonballs as it has in the gun (limit is still 42);

### 'Multiwave' Triple Shotgun:

-Each Cannonball deals 6 damage to all mobs;

-13 blocks range;

-The player can add as many Cannonballs as it has in the gun (limit is still 42);

-The waves are now faster and deadlier, but the player will move slower after it used the gun and the gun is slower to reload;

### Tikelatos Blowpipe:

-Changed how it shoots (again): it shoots instantly now;

-20 blocks range(instead of staying up for 1.25 seconds);

-Clayballs now need to be put on the 9th hotbar slot in order to use the blowpipe;

-Clayballs now deal 2 damage to all mobs;

-Added 3 new clayballs: Weakness Clayball (applies weakness), Wither Clayball (applies wither), Cursed Clayball(applies wither, slowness and weakness for longer duration);

-Doubled its durability;

### AFT-95:

-150 blocks range;

-Deals 20 explosive damage to all mobs (less if entity has blast resistance);

-Added fire particles to the launched shell;

### 'Guided' AFT-95:

-Added a dummy of the player when it launches the 'guided' shell, as the player's 'point of return' (if hit, the player will return to its 'point of return' and the shell will travel in the direction the player fixed it);

-If the player crouches while 'guiding' the shell, it will go back to its 'point of return' and the shell will travel in the direction the player fixed it;

-Movement of the 'guided' shell is more optimized now;

-Removed the range limit of the 'guided' shell;

-300 blocks range;

-Deals 20 explosive damage to all mobs (less if entity has blast resistance);

-Added fire and rocket particles to the launched 'guided' shell;

### Bang Piztol:

-Bang Pistol has been renamed Bang Piztol;

### 'Prank' Bang Piztol:

-'Prank' Bang Pistol has been renamed 'Prank' Bang Piztol;

-45 blocks range;

-Deals 20 explosive damage to all mobs (less if entity has blast resistance);

### Mini-gunzt:

-Changed the 'look' of the Mini-gunzt;

-Changed how it shoots: it shoots instantly now;

-The player can shoot the gun now by holding it, and the gun has a new spray pattern;

-The player can partially reload the gun by throwing it, while holding Small Bullets in the offhand and crouching (it can only reload if the player has 450 ammo or lower);

-Max ammo is now 600;

-50 blocks range;

-Deals 4 damage to all mobs;

### Mini-gunzt (AFT Skin):

-Changed the 'look' of the Mini-gunzt (AFT);

-Changed how it shoots: it shoots instantly now;

-The player can shoot the gun now by holding it, and the gun has a new spray pattern;

-Every 3rd bullet will be an Ancient Fire Turtle Shell which will explode (players don't count);

-The player can partially reload the gun by throwing it, while holding Small Bullets in the offhand and crouching (it can only reload if the player has 450 ammo or lower);

-Max ammo is now 600;

-50 blocks range;

-Deals 4 damage to all mobs and the 3rd bullet deals 8 damage;

### 'Ash'thrower:

-Changed how it shoots: it shoots instantly now;

-35 blocks range;

-The player will blind and NEW confuse the enemy for 5 seconds (the enemy will spin and cannot move);

-The player can partially reload the gun by crouching and throwing it at the same time;

-Changed from 3 total ammo to 20 (to match the values with the gun ammo);

-1.5 seconds cooldown and 5 seconds reload cooldown;

### Woodanlanchops Grenade:

-Summons the 'Woodanlan Witch' above the grenade that snares and deals 12 damage to all mobs(good luck killing a boss with this);


# In the end

-Many other bugs/glitches got fixed.

<br><br><br>

This datapack is compatible only for Minecraft 1.20.1 and above!

Older datapack versions are compatible for Minecraft 1.13 and above (will be available here someday)!

This datapack is Multiplayer-compatible!

If you are using the datapack in a video, make sure to credit me and my work!

'Allow Cheats' **MUST BE ON** in order for everything to work properly!

If there are bugs and glitches found in the datapack, comment the issue down below, check the report bug/glitch website: hehegamingandy38.wixsite.com/mydatapacks/report-bug or contact me on Discord(@hehegamingandy)!

If you try the BETA and Pre-Release Versions, do not download them in the same world (it can cause bugs and errors between items)!

Hope you enjoy it!
